data.description: This is it! A Beautiful rare well-kept townhome in sought after Upper Marlboro!! This 2 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom open floorplan masterpiece, is the perfect property for a single buyer, couple looking for great space, or a growing family that needs spacious rooms. Park your car in your private garage and avoid the hassles of curbside availability. As you easily access your home from the garage, or front entry, you’ll walk into a beautiful open floorplan main level oasis with a relaxing fireplace and hardwood flooring. Enjoy cooking meals for your family and friends in your spacious bar top kitchen with upgraded countertops and beautiful appliances. With just a few steps you can take a break after a long day work on your private balcony with a cool beverage of choice or entertaining in your loft/den. This property has 2 bedrooms on the upper level including a master suite with a beautifully tiled shower and tub, while also easily accommodating a king size bed with plenty of space to give. Upstairs laundry room is conveniently located just steps away from the bedroom doors. Don't let this property get away; It is truly a hidden gem at a fair and reasonable price. This lovely 2 story 2 Bedroom 2.5 bath home is conveniently located to all transportation, shopping and recreation facilities. Also, the home has a New (2023) A/C unit, washer, refrigerator, garbage disposal and garage door.
